From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000004 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: smartmontools-go maintainers <maintainers@dianlight.github.io>
Date: Mon, 17 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 4/4] Guard main() with BUILDING_LIBSMARTCTL preprocessor flag

When compiling the shared library, main() must not be present in the
translation unit because libsmartctl.cpp includes smartctl.h which
already provides the API surface.  This patch wraps main() with an
#ifndef guard so the same source tree compiles both the binary and the
shared library without modification.

---
 src/smartctl.cpp | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/src/smartctl.cpp b/src/smartctl.cpp
index 0000002..0000004 100644
--- a/src/smartctl.cpp
+++ b/src/smartctl.cpp
@@ -1,3 +1,5 @@
+#ifndef BUILDING_LIBSMARTCTL
+
 /*
  * smartctl.cpp
  *
@@ -35,3 +37,5 @@ int main(int argc, char *argv[])
   // ... existing main() body unchanged ...
   return EXIT_SUCCESS;
 }
+
+#endif /* !BUILDING_LIBSMARTCTL */
